  "prompt": "Which earphones are better under 2000?",
  "response": "There are several great options for earphones under \u20b92000 in India as of my last update. Here are some popular choices that offer good sound quality, comfort, and additional features:\n\n1. **Realme Buds 2** - Known for their good sound quality, sturdy build, and tangle-free design, these are a popular choice among budget users.\n\n2. **Xiaomi Redmi Earbuds S** - These truly wireless earbuds are praised for their decent sound quality, low latency, and good battery life.\n\n3. **Boat Bassheads 100** - These wired earphones offer good bass, comfort, and durability. They are very affordable and a favorite among budget-conscious users.\n\n4. **Sony WI-C200** - While they might be slightly over \u20b92000 during sales, they offer great sound quality, battery life, and comfort for an affordable price.\n\n5. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush** - These earbuds offer a balance of features including good sound quality, a comfortable fit, and decent battery life.\n\n6. **Boult Audio ProBass Bluetooth Earphones** - These wireless earphones come with a magnetic design and are known for their bass-heavy sound.\n\n7. **OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z** - If you can find them under \u20b92000 during sales or promotions, these offer great sound and quick charging features.\n\nWhen choosing earphones, consider factors like sound quality, comfort, build quality, and additional features like noise cancellation or waterproofing. Always check for latest reviews and user feedback to ensure you're getting a suitable product for your needs.",
